data.description: The Property is located in the heart of Hampton. 5 minutes away from Downtown Hampton, with close access to shopping, entertainment and plenty of restaurants. Less than a 10 minute drive to Fort Monroe beach & National Monument. 4 bedrooms with 2 full baths with bonus rooms. This home is just over 2000 sqft. Roof, Windows & HVAC Unit about 3 years old. Come see it today!!
